## Section 35: Anti-Patterns Consolidated

### 35.1 Component Anti-Patterns

❌ **Prop Drilling (more than 3 levels)**
```tsx
// BAD
<App user={user}>
  <Dashboard user={user}>
    <TransactionList user={user}>
      <Transaction user={user} />

// GOOD - Use Context
const UserContext = createContext();
<UserContext.Provider value={user}>
  <App />
</UserContext.Provider>
```

❌ **Inline Styles Over Utility Classes**
```tsx
// BAD
<div style={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)', padding: '24px' }}>

// GOOD
<div className="bg-white/10 p-6">
```

❌ **Not Using Component Composition**
```tsx
// BAD - Monolithic component
const Dashboard = () => (
  <div>
    {/* 500 lines of JSX */}
  </div>
);

// GOOD - Composed from smaller pieces
const Dashboard = () => (
  <DashboardLayout>
    <StatsGrid />
    <RevenueChart />
    <TransactionsList />
  </DashboardLayout>
);
```

### 35.2 Performance Anti-Patterns

❌ **Not Memoizing Expensive Calculations**
```tsx
// BAD
const filteredData = transactions.filter(expensive_operation);

// GOOD
const filteredData = useMemo(
  () => transactions.filter(expensive_operation),
  [transactions]
);
```

❌ **Creating Functions in Render**
```tsx
// BAD
<Button onClick={() => handleClick(item.id)}>

// GOOD
const handleClick = useCallback((id) => {
  // Handle click
}, []);
<Button onClick={() => handleClick(item.id)}>
```

### 35.3 Accessibility Anti-Patterns

❌ **Missing Alt Text**
```tsx
// BAD
<img src="logo.png" />

// GOOD
<img src="logo.png" alt="SabPaisa logo" />
```

❌ **Non-Semantic Buttons**
```tsx
// BAD
<div onClick={handleClick}>Click me</div>

// GOOD
<button onClick={handleClick}>Click me</button>
```

❌ **Missing ARIA Labels**
```tsx
// BAD
<button><X /></button>

// GOOD
<button aria-label="Close modal"><X /></button>
```

### 35.4 State Management Anti-Patterns

❌ **Not Cleaning Up Side Effects**
```tsx
// BAD
useEffect(() => {
  const timer = setInterval(() => {}, 1000);
}, []);

// GOOD
useEffect(() => {
  const timer = setInterval(() => {}, 1000);
  return () => clearInterval(timer); // Cleanup
}, []);
```

❌ **Mutating State Directly**
```tsx
// BAD
const handleUpdate = () => {
  user.name = 'New Name';
  setUser(user);
};

// GOOD
const handleUpdate = () => {
  setUser({ ...user, name: 'New Name' });
};
```

